<div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md max-w-3xl mx-auto mt-8">
  <!-- Business Overview Section -->
  <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-6">About Perfume Paradise</h1>
  
  <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-4">
    Perfume Paradise is a boutique perfume retailer based in Winnipeg, Manitoba, specializing in a wide range of high-quality fragrances for both men and women. 
    With a dedicated team of 10 employees, Perfume Paradise has been operational for over 5 years, building a loyal customer base through personalized service and expert fragrance advice. 
    Our physical store, located in a popular shopping district, allows customers to experience the world of fragrance firsthand. Additionally, we participate in local markets and events to bring our unique offerings to a wider audience.
  </p>

  <!-- Products Offered Section -->
  <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Products Offered</h2>
  <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-4">
    Perfume Paradise is expanding its reach by establishing an online store, offering a curated selection of perfumes including designer brands, niche fragrances, and custom blends. 
    Our online store will feature detailed product descriptions, customer reviews, and personalized recommendations based on your fragrance preferences.
  </p>

  <!-- Target Demographic Section -->
  <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Target Demographic</h2>
  <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-6">
    Our target demographic includes both men and women aged 18-45 who appreciate high-quality fragrances and seek unique scent options. 
    They value personal expression through fragrance and are likely to purchase online for convenience and exclusivity.
  </p>

  <!-- Admin Edit Link -->
